        <h2>Idlenet (WIP)</h2>
        <p>Idlenet is an incremental game that is currently in-development. It's about managing a growing network. I consider it my first “proper” game, made with LÖVE2D in Lua. My plan is to release it for Windows, MacOS, Linux, and web browsers, on itch.io and Steam. The game's source will also “soon” be available on Github.</p>
